reviewText: Calling this a bad movie is an insult to bad movies. A weak story, bad dialogue, and bad acting add up to a film with no redeeming qualities. Some funny bits in the MST3K version, but otherwise don't waste your time.
this is like a B movie with space aliens in it. some young guy finds a space alien weapon and uses it and it turns him into one of the space aliens as he uses it . its cool movie
